In the home purchase market, buyers are becoming more accepting of stabilizing 7% interest rates.  This proves the case that the cost of originating mortgages can \(and should\) come down in order to pass these savings down to these potential homeowners.

We're low on inventory and also high on demand in larger metropolitan statistical areas.  AI-powered solutions like @[TidalWave](urn:li:organization:94119582) will be helping keep costs at bay & strong real estate partners busy!

